（悲鳴）

32
00:02:06,167 --> 00:02:08,336
Oh fuck... Oh fuck...

33
00:02:15,135 --> 00:02:16,094
（叫び声）

34
00:02:17,011 --> 00:02:18,221
（ブラウン）We'd better run!

35
